<plot>Knowing that a process server is waiting for him at work, Leon stays home while his wife takes his place at the office. While Leon is making a shambles out of his homework chores, his wife is at the office making friends with the process server, who pretends to be an old college chum of Leon's. Mrs. Erroll invites him home for dinner, where he serves the papers on Leon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?244044</url></doc>
